title: Dubstep Cat
description: For licensing/usage please contact: licensing(at)jukinvideo.com Thanks so much to everyone!!! I have my own music project - Check it out here!! http://www.youtube.com/winfieldmusic1 Meet Dubstep Cat! He was a stray that my room mate took in and we take care of him at our apartment. He is the chillest cat ever, especially for a stray! He is the friendliest cat I have ever met and loves attention from people. Some have speculated that I was harming him in this video, but I know my relationship with him, and trust me, he was fine playing like this, and I didn't harm him in any way. My friend and I were listening to dubstep and playing with our cat and he started to make him dance, so, we decided to film it. Enjoy! The song is Benny Benassi ft. Gary Go - Cinema (Skrillex Remix) Thanks for watching! =] Check out my other videos, I rarely do cat videos. I'm mainly focusing on filming music videos. I have my own music project - Check it out here!! http://www.youtube.com/winfieldmusic1 I do a mixture of electronic and acoustic. Right now I am doing cover songs while finishing up my first self produced album. I do all my own video editing and audio recording. instagram: @THEWINFIELD1 twitter: @dubstepcatx facebook: /wesleywinfieldbower
